{{Databox}}'''Lmsɛudi Muḥmmad''' amara d umdyaz [[Lmɣrib|amrruki]], ilul g usggʷas n 1991 ɣ udwwaṛ n Umdiɣr g tsga n tɣiwant n Tmzgadiwin, illan g tqbilt n [[Ilbnsirn]] tasga n [[Imi n Tanut]], [[Cicawa]].

Ig asdawi ɣ tmassanin tasusyulujiyin g [[Tasdawit n Bnu Zuhr|tsdawit n Ibn Zuhr]] g [[Agadir|Ugadir]].

== Tismɣurin ==
Yura kṛaḍ idlisn s tutlayt tamaziɣt, yumẓ kigan n tsmɣurin tinamurin.

* Yumẓ tasmɣurt n tbadut 2m tv ɣ usggʷas n 2012, ɣ tskla n iɛrrimn.
* Yumẓ tasmɣurt n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt ɣ usggʷas n 2019.
* Yumẓ  tasmɣurt n tussna tamaziɣt n usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt asggʷas n 2020.

== Idlisn ==
Idlisn lli yura umara amaziɣ Lmsɛudi Muḥmmad:

* Adlis n tmzgunt - [[Taydrt n uswingm|''Taydrt n uswingm'']] - d iffɣ nn ɣ usggʷas n 2019, Tssufɣ t id tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt. lli yumẓn tasmɣurt n tskla tamaziɣt n [[Asinag Agldan n Tussna Tamaziɣt|usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt,]] ɣ usggʷas n 2020, ɣ anaw n tskla n umẓyan.
* Adlis n tullisin timaziɣin igzzuln - [[Ixf n ungi|''Ixf n ungi'']] - d iffɣ nn ɣ usggʷas n 2021, issufɣ t id [[Asinag Agldan n Tussna Tamaziɣt|usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt]], isman 18 n tullist tamaziɣt bḍan t awal f kigan n untimn imaynutn.
* Adlis n tmdyazin - ''[[Amwan n wawal]]'' - iffɣ d ɣ usggʷas n 2015, yumẓ tasmɣurt n tbadut tis snat n usnflul n tskla n iɛrrimn  ɣ usggʷas n 2013. Isman kigan n tmdyazin isawaln f kṛaḍ wantimn : tamagit - tudrt - tayri.

